  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110127118719\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110127118719\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p>예약시간이 5분정도 지난 시간.</p>\r\n<p>추나예약 환자분이 헐레벌떡 들어오면서 \"메리크리스마스~\" 하시면서 건네주셨습니다.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d6303b4f4c5b8269.jpg\" width=\"462\" height=\"615\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 462px; rheight: 615px\" id=\"20111222_240/isuhani_13245428759349q0bn_JPEG/%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8_%C5%A9%B8%AE%BD%BA%B8%B6%BD%BA_%C4%C9%C0%CD.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A416797F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d6303b4f4c5b8269.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>너무 이쁘죠^^ (선물해주신 환자분이 더 이뻐요!!)</p>\r\n<p>요즘엔 항상 감사할 일 뿐이네요!!</p>\r\n<p>이수한의원에 와주시는 분들 모두 감사합니다!!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>MERRY CHRISTMAS~</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
